LIBRARY STDCXX
PPDEFINE BITTREE

REQUIRES ./c_source

CHILDORDER localAPI


D gr_btDistributedSort If both gr_btSortByWork and gr_btCustomWork are True,
D & controls behavior of the sorting algorithm. True = Uses less local
D & storage but increases communication. False (default) = Uses less
D & communication but high memory consumption.
PARAMETER gr_btDistributedSort BOOLEAN False

D gr_btExchangeBflags True = PM-specific array bflags is exchanged during
D & refinement. Increases communication. False (default) = entire bflags array
D & is reset to -1 during each refinement.
PARAMETER gr_btExchangeBflags BOOLEAN False
